
# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.2.0] - 2024-02-28
### Changed
    Changed entities-based events and systems to bundle-based


## [0.1.9] - 2024-02-28
### Added
    Added function to call for CreateOrModify action
### Changed
    Changed parent_child example to use CreateOrModify action


## [0.1.8] - 2024-02-28
### Added
    Added a CreateOrModify action to create an entity if it does not exist or modify it if it does.

## [0.1.7] - 2024-02-27
### Added
    Despawn child entity if parent cannot be found

## [0.1.6] - 2024-02-06
### Changed
    Changed event parameter from component to entity to allow entities with multiple components

## [0.1.5] - 2024-01-30
### Added
    More documentations on code
### Changed
    Changed events to in-method commands rather than direct struct composing
    Provide more details for logging

## [0.1.4] - 2024-01-27

### Added
    Added a system to clear child entities based on parent's lifetime with an example.
    Added a `Clear` action to parent's event to clear all children on event trigger.

### Changed
    Optimized cargo.toml dependencies

## [0.1.3] - 2024-01-27

### Changed
    Added a function to get component using the Identifier

## [0.1.2] - 2024-01-27

### Changed
    Changed lifetime trait function to non-reference

## [0.1.1] - 2024-01-27

### Added
    Added a lifetime feature
    - Added a BioglocalTrait for lifetime specification
    - Added a system to act as a garbage collector

## [0.1.0] - 2024-01-27

### Added
    Released first version of bevy_family
    - Allow easy creation, updating, and removal of parent-child components with events
    - Using resource to keep track of history of events